      <abstract id="aspace_aae7315d860f7a4759d42bad1610a909">Giles House is a student residence hall
        on East Campus. Contains the records of Giles House, a residence hall for students at Duke
        University. Types of materials include correspondence, minutes, and a record of visitors.
        Topics of materials include student life, Duke University history, residential living, and
        women college students. Materials range in date from 1932-1980. The bulk of the material
        ranges in date from 1961-1966.</abstract>
